{"tid":1136272,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"買車 上會 保險問題","createTime":"2019-05-03T01:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T00:44:45.000Z","uid":133436,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"870d03af3d82acefdf1dcff7c072a3e70af68d8a","tid":1136272,"uid":133436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T01:45:05.000Z","msg":"各位師兄 近期小弟計劃買車 但有保險及車保問題都幾煩惱<br />\n<br />\n因為我本人係上唔到會 如果架車用我名就一定要full pay (但我prefer 分3年還部份車款，因利息都唔算太貴） 想問，全新車(bmw) 有冇好似出面車行咁現金價 上會價？<br />\n<br />\n因以上問題，令到我有諗過用女朋友名義上會，收入支出應該計到 （佢冇債務） 但佢牌齡唔足 (現有p1年 + 正式牌1年），出保險好似會貴（有有師兄知大約幾多？）又令到我自己儲唔到ncb 但就可以分期部份車款。<br />\n<br />\n兩個都過左25 均無NCB 如借錢應該會借 20-25萬，車價50萬 <br />\n我已足牌齡  <br />\n<br />\n正評：Full pay 自己名<br />\n負評：女朋友名 上會 買貴保險<br />\n<br />\n求各位大神插細力d 未試過買車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e941917c893a36d42b694dfc92dbb3778c2cd936","tid":1136272,"uid":97104,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T01:46:37.000Z","msg":"Full pay<br />\n女朋友不是老婆"},{"pid":"6f8b655b7df27dc2e8c5c586c654cd509fe312e7","tid":1136272,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T01:53:42.000Z","msg":"足牌齡買新車上唔到會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主信貸評級F?"},{"pid":"b5644d07ab696260767b6af05b7876c51f2305ef","tid":1136272,"uid":133436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f8b655b7df27dc2e8c5c586c654cd509fe312e7","tid":1136272,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T01:53:42.000Z","msg":"足牌齡買新車上唔到會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主信貸評級F?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:07:06.000Z","msg":"因有其他債務係身 tu 係 A"},{"pid":"d1cc91fcae6390690c033f6d1140a246d93f7256","tid":1136272,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5644d07ab696260767b6af05b7876c51f2305ef","tid":1136272,"uid":133436,"like":0,